ActExport and Import Permits Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Import Control List
PrecisOrder Amending the IMPORT CONTROL LIST (ICL) in order to (1) amend the ICL in order to add Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement import Origin Quotas-eligible goods to the ICL; (2) remove imports controls for certain beef and veal, as well as milk protein substances; and 3) update the Harmonized System codes or descriptions for certain ICL items.
